{"tid":1342612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府又強烈譴責暴力行為,但係上環同元朗擺埋一齊啊!!!","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:07:53.000Z","uid":163028,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"40b214971a95f7aba146e8999ac6a16901916a8a","tid":1342612,"uid":163028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:46:18.000Z","msg":"勁嬲!!!呢野有冇得搞!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/22/P2019072200010.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F22%2FP2019072200010.htm&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1NLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=e37c8a88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/22/P2019072200010.htm</a><br />\n政府強烈譴責暴力行為<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  就昨日（七月二十一日）晚上在上環及元朗發生的暴力行為，特區政府作以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n  繼之前衝擊中聯辦大樓後，再有激進示威者無視警方多次警告，在上環一帶向警方發動連番暴力襲擊，包括投擲汽油彈、縱火、擲磚，亦堵塞主要幹道，行為令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n  與此同時，在元朗有人聚眾在港鐵車站月台及車廂內襲擊乘客，引發衝突，導致有人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n  香港作為法治社會完全不能容忍任何暴力行為，特區政府予以強烈譴責，並會嚴正追究。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月22日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間0時16分"},{"pid":"5458db5cd590ce3a61539edef82ee64ba8315891","tid":1342612,"uid":163028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7d37830de64250cb52669c3846c94aa761f7c8","tid":1342612,"uid":163028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307932326d6c580f9c73fdac469170cbdfa9